  "title": "🧠 Events & Marketing (Personal Development)",
  "description": "<p>📍 Singapore | Full-Time | Entry-Level</p><p>This role goes beyond sales. You’ll develop confidence, communication, discipline, and leadership — skills that last a lifetime.</p><p>Royal Organisation invests heavily in <strong>personal development workshops, coaching, and mindset training</strong>, helping individuals grow both professionally and personally.</p><p><strong>Ideal for:</strong> Individuals committed to self-improvement and long-term growth.<br /><br /><strong>Requirements / What We’re Looking For</strong></p><p><ul><li>🌱 Growth-oriented and self-motivated</li><li>🔄 Open to stepping outside comfort zone</li><li>🔥 Driven to improve personally and professionally</li></ul></p><p><strong>Responsibilities / What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><p><ul><li>🗣 Build confidence through customer engagement</li><li>🎤 Develop communication & presentation skills</li><li>📚 Perform ethical sales technique for our clients</li></ul></p><p><strong>Benefits / What You’ll Gain</strong></p><p><ul><li>🧠 Strong mindset and confidence development</li><li>🎓 Personal development coaching</li><li>🚀 Long-term career and life skills</li></ul></p>",
